### 8.8  A jazzed Twinkle — the finale

Let's take the Twinkle Twinkle melody (you know it from Ch3) and dress it in a jazz timbre. We'll use:
- The jazz-piano voice from 8.5 (warm harmonics, percussive ADSR, gentle low-pass).
- A walking bassline (root motion in quarter notes, staccato envelope).
- Swing rhythm (triplet subdivision, 2:1 long-short; we'll approximate with manual timing shifts for now, since swing quantization is *[needs: GAP-1]* for proper triplet control).

**Twinkle Twinkle in C, jazzed:**

```scheme
;; Jazz piano voice (from 8.5).
(define jazz-piano
  (let ((v (voice/create 'jazz-piano)))
    (voice/waveform v (createPeriodicWave (list 1.0 0.5 0.3 0.15 0.08 0.04)))
    (voice/envelope v (adsr 0.02 0.15 0.4 0.1))
    (voice/filter v 'lowpass 3500 0.7)
    v))

;; Staccato bass voice (same harmonic profile, shorter envelope).
(define jazz-bass
  (let ((v (voice/create 'jazz-bass)))
    (voice/waveform v (createPeriodicWave (list 1.0 0.5 0.3 0.15)))
    (voice/envelope v (adsr 0.01 0.05 0.2 0.05))
    (voice/filter v 'lowpass 2500 0.5)
    v))

;; Twinkle melody (C C G G A A G, F F E E D D C).
;; Measures 1–2:
(note/strike 'C4 'quarter 0.7 jazz-piano)
(at-beat 1 (note/strike 'C4 'quarter 0.7 jazz-piano))
(at-beat 2 (note/strike 'G4 'quarter 0.7 jazz-piano))
(at-beat 3 (note/strike 'G4 'quarter 0.7 jazz-piano))

(at-beat 4 (note/strike 'A4 'quarter 0.7 jazz-piano))
(at-beat 5 (note/strike 'A4 'quarter 0.7 jazz-piano))
(at-beat 6 (note/strike 'G4 'half 0.7 jazz-piano))

;; Measures 3–4:
(at-beat 8 (note/strike 'F4 'quarter 0.7 jazz-piano))
(at-beat 9 (note/strike 'F4 'quarter 0.7 jazz-piano))
(at-beat 10 (note/strike 'E4 'quarter 0.7 jazz-piano))
(at-beat 11 (note/strike 'E4 'quarter 0.7 jazz-piano))

(at-beat 12 (note/strike 'D4 'quarter 0.7 jazz-piano))
(at-beat 13 (note/strike 'D4 'quarter 0.7 jazz-piano))
(at-beat 14 (note/strike 'C4 'half 0.7 jazz-piano))

;; Walking bassline (root motion, quarter notes): C2, C2, G2, G2, A2, A2, G2, G2, F2, F2, E2, E2, D2, D2, C2, C2.
(note/strike 'C2 'quarter 0.65 jazz-bass)
(at-beat 1 (note/strike 'C2 'quarter 0.65 jazz-bass))
(at-beat 2 (note/strike 'G2 'quarter 0.65 jazz-bass))
(at-beat 3 (note/strike 'G2 'quarter 0.65 jazz-bass))

